{"title":"About this blog","date":"2019-07-25T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 25, 2019","L":"07/25/2019","MM-DD":"07-25"},"updated":"2021-01-05T20:05:23.089Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>嘿，你来啦！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"关于博客\">关于博客<a title=\"#关于博客\" href=\"#关于博客\"></a></h2>\n<p>鼓捣了一个多星期，一定要长期写下去啊</p>\n<h3 id=\"搭建流程\">搭建流程<a title=\"#搭建流程\" href=\"#搭建流程\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>使用<a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\">hexo</a>搭建</li>\n<li>主题采用了<a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Elmore Cheng</a>同学的模版：<a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">inside</a></li>\n<li>网站资源托管在<a href=\"https://pages.github.com/\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub Pages</a>上\n<ul>\n<li>为了更好的速度已迁移到<a href=\"https://console.cloud.tencent.com/cos\" target=\"_blank\">腾讯云对象存储</a></li>\n<li>由于更新速度原因又迁回了<a href=\"https://pages.github.com/\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub Pages</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- - 由[Algolia](https://www.algolia.com/)提供搜索服务 -->\n<ul>\n<li>使用<a href=\"https://valine.js.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Valine</a>评论系统并用<a href=\"https://github.com/DesertsP/Valine-Admin\" target=\"_blank\">Valine admin</a>管理。</li>\n<li>访问次数统计: <a href=\"http://busuanzi.ibruce.info/\" target=\"_blank\">不算子</a>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这个次数统计还有些问题，刷新三次一次正常一次一直在加载一次就直接消失了…<br>\n[2020.03.29] 原来是我 script 标签引入有问题，其实就是个简单的跨域问题，已解决</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"图床\">图床<a title=\"#图床\" href=\"#图床\"></a></h3>\n<p>刚接触<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/markdown/3245829?fr=aladdin\" target=\"_blank\">MarkDown</a>记笔记的时候准备的图床————<a href=\"https://console.cloud.tencent.com/cos\" target=\"_blank\">腾讯云对象存储</a>，貌似是赠送50G存储空间（免费额度最近有调整），目前每个月还送10G流量（并不是人人都送，但是现在注册账号的话应该会送），可以配置默认的CDN加速域名，做个人博客或md文档的图床足够用了，建议分几个储存桶，个人博客桶开启防盗链设置（只有自己的域名才能请求到数据），这样别人想用你的图片就只能自己保存而不能直接复制链接放在自己博客里（毕竟流量是<s>花钱</s>的）。但也有个缺点就是本地服务器也不能加载图片，调试的时候不太方便。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[2020.03.29] 仔细读了读<a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">inside</a>主题文档才发现其实作者已经设置了CDN域名的动态渲染，这样在配置里面改一处就可以实现全局的改动了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"内容与写作\">内容与写作<a title=\"#内容与写作\" href=\"#内容与写作\"></a></h3>\n<p>主要分享一些平时学习时候整理的笔记。目前原创内容还比较少（太菜</p>\n<p>19年8月之前的文章都是以前整理的笔记改版过来的。以前整理的时候就是为了记录一下，并没有考虑读者的感受所以可能有些地方会比较费解，如果真的感兴趣的话还是建议去教程视频吧，如果想要MarkDown源文件整理自己的笔记也可以联系我。</p>\n<p>写作以 MarkDown 为主，辅以 HTML 和 CSS，编辑器还是推荐<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com\" target=\"_blank\">VSCode</a>，好用而且跨平台，以前只有Windows系统的时候主机装 MarkDownPad 死活装不上，过了好久才想起来直接用 VSCode 不就结了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"关于主题\">关于主题<a title=\"#关于主题\" href=\"#关于主题\"></a></h3>\n<p>使用版本：<a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside/releases/tag/2.6.4\" target=\"_blank\">2.6.4</a></p>\n<p>主题用的是<a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Elmore Cheng</a>同学的模版：<a href=\"https://github.com/ikeq/hexo-theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">inside</a></p>\n<p>主题的官方说明在这里：<a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside</a></p>\n<p>进行了一些个性化的配置，改了一下文章的宽度和post图片的高度，因为我比较多是在笔记本和台式机上看所以如果固定px宽度很难同时适应13寸和27寸的屏幕，在 <code>theme/inside/_config.yml</code> 中做如下设置：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">appearance:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># Maximum width of content</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">  content_width:</span> <span class=\"number\">80</span><span class=\"string\">%</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">plugins:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">  - tag:</span> <span class=\"string\">style</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    code:</span> <span class=\"string\">|</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">      @media screen and (min-width:500px) &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">        .φcu &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span><span class=\"attr\">          max-height:</span> <span class=\"number\">300</span><span class=\"string\">px!important;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"string\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"string\">@media</span> <span class=\"string\">screen</span> <span class=\"string\">and</span> <span class=\"string\">(min-width:800px)</span> <span class=\"string\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">.φcu</span> <span class=\"string\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">          max-height:</span> <span class=\"number\">400</span><span class=\"string\">px!important;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"string\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"string\">@media</span> <span class=\"string\">screen</span> <span class=\"string\">and</span> <span class=\"string\">(min-width:1100px)</span> <span class=\"string\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">.φcu</span> <span class=\"string\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">          max-height:</span> <span class=\"number\">500</span><span class=\"string\">px!important;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"string\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"string\">@media</span> <span class=\"string\">screen</span> <span class=\"string\">and</span> <span class=\"string\">(min-width:1400px)</span> <span class=\"string\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">.φcu</span> <span class=\"string\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">          max-height:</span> <span class=\"number\">600</span><span class=\"string\">px!important;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"string\">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"关于博主\">关于博主<a title=\"#关于博主\" href=\"#关于博主\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong>准</strong>程序猿，对机械有浓厚兴趣，但是在姐姐的强力干预下读了计算机<s>真香</s>。现居北京。<br>\n一年前（今天2019.8.14）开始自己做项目，目前主攻前端，擅长微信小程序开发。希望能逐步加深对编程的理解。左边有我的联系方式（手机端可以左滑或从右下角三个点点那里进入），欢迎各位小伙伴评论/交流。</p>\n","link":"about","comments":true,"plink":"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/about/","toc":[{"id":"关于博客","title":"关于博客","index":"1","children":[{"id":"搭建流程","title":"搭建流程","index":"1.1"},{"id":"图床","title":"图床","index":"1.2"},{"id":"内容与写作","title":"内容与写作","index":"1.3"},{"id":"关于主题","title":"关于主题","index":"1.4"}]},{"id":"关于博主","title":"关于博主","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Vincente Liang","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/about/\" title=\"About this blog\">https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/about/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"July 25, 2019","updated":"January 5, 2021"}}